to make any project you need to follow the given project structure for the sdk to buil simply.

	project directory--
					   |
					   |
					   -------dir one
					   |
					   |
					   -------dir two
					   |
					   |
					   ------CMakeList.txt
					   |
					   |
					   ------(all other 3 files that are required for cmake)


for setting baud rate of serial connection use 
	$stty -F /dev/<ttydevicename> speed <speed required>

